    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>Her Name</strong>, a 2D platformer and puzzle game where every movement, every silence, and every light tells a story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guided by a mysterious sphere sliding along its rails, move in synergy with it to uncover the fears, doubts, and dreams of a character searching for meaning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The game never speaks.<br>It shows.<br>It listens.<br>And it invites you to do the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With no dialogue, <strong>Her Name</strong> asks you to observe the world, read between gestures, and interpret symbols. Explore six thematic chapters, navigate 39 puzzle levels, solve over a hundred challenges, and discover 31 scripted narrative stages that slowly assemble a fragile, complex, and essential love story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 24 hidden objects, unravel the mysteries of reality and dreams, and accompany the character to the heart of what haunts him… and what keeps him standing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore his dreams. Face his fears. And finally discover… her name.</strong></p>",
